  <article class="static-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="static-page__lang-switch"><a href="https://freelife50.com/privacy-policy/">このページを日本語で読む</a></p>
    <p>Ramen, Beer & Blog (https://freelife50.com/) respects the protection of personal information and operates this website under the following policy.</p>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>This website may use third-party advertising services. Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this and other websites.</p>
    <p>Ads may be delivered based on information about visits to this and other sites. Users can disable cookies through their browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>This website uses Google Analytics to understand site traffic. Google Analytics uses cookies and collects access data in a way that does not personally identify users.</p>
    <p>The collected data is used to improve the website, understand which articles are being read, and improve display quality.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Information provided through contact is used only for replies and communication related to the inquiry. It will not be used for unrelated purposes.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>While this website strives to provide accurate information, it does not guarantee the accuracy or safety of the content. This website is not responsible for damages or losses caused by the information published here.</p>

    <h2>Copyright</h2>
    <p>Unauthorized reproduction of text, images, and other content on this website is prohibited. When quoting content, please clearly indicate the source and stay within the scope permitted by copyright law.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>This policy may be changed without prior notice when necessary. Changes become effective when posted on this page.</p>

    <p class="static-page__updated">Established: May 9, 2026</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
